                            <comment id="13640702" author="vaidya" created="Wed, 24 Apr 2013 17:39:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
I think there&apos;s one big caveat with the new implementation &amp;#8211; we shouldn&apos;t have anyone call OperationManager.closeOperation() directly; they should always go through a HiveSession object.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
